Maintainer: Devon Ash <dash@clearpathrobotics.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), ros-melodic-catkin
Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/rosatomic
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-melodic-rosatomic
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
Description: rosatomic provides the C++11-style atomic operations by pulling symbols from the proposed Boost.Atomic package into the ros namespace.
 Once C++11-style atomics (std::atomic) are available from compilers, rosatomic will conditionally use those instead.
